CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 9, 1964, pg. 1 reads:" World-Wide Delegation - The nearly 900 delegates attending the Methodist General Conference in Pittsburgh is world-wide, representing many races that inhabit the globe. The Courier cameraman captured some of these in above picture...Extreme right, Rev. Miguel de Andrade, Angola, Africa; Mrs. R. E. Dodge, South Rhodesia, and Adriano Kapangue, Angola, Africa.-Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Reverend Miguel de Andrade and Adriano Kapangue, posed in interior during the 1964 United Methodist Church General Conference
